Breakfast is not great. Lunch and dinner better.

Price very competitive from us$4 upwards you can get meal with drink
I and my friend had a dinner here tonight.  Not too crowded.  Taste not too bad.  We have a good time :)
Good comfort Cantonese dished

Never the breakfast
Absolutely rubbish food and service
Rude staff

People were tough with this place. It was not a 5 but definitely a solid 4. Portions were big. Had fried rice noodles with fish and steamed pork patty. You get free rice and soup with steamed pork patty (and some other dishes) after 6pm!! Value! Servers were nice. No 10%. Free tea!

result.formatted_address: 25, 23 Centre St, Sai Ying Pun, 香港
result.name: Tsui Yuen

reviews.text: 真係好普通😥😥
週末晚上十時後光顧，點了豉椒鮮魷炒麵、豉油皇炒麵、浄雲呑和清炒菜心共四道菜，每款菜式味道及賣相不錯，份量足本，店内裝修新，坐得舒服，招呼也不錯，在這個地區及晚上時間來說，不失為吃飯消遣的好地方。可惜廁所環境較差，地面濕滑兼放置太多雜物，令人對餐廳整體印象大打折扣，希望盡快改善。
貴 ， 唔抵食 never come here again. Poor food quality, overpriced
我食咗個午餐，食物品質一般，但杯奶茶就幾好味！
